<div class="row">
  <div class="h2 mb-5 mx-5 text-center w-100 border-bottom border-darkorange py-2">Profile</div>
  <div class="col-9 text-center mx-auto">
    <%= form_for @profile do |f| %>
      <%= render 'shared/devise_errormes', object: f.object %>

      <div class="form_control mb-4">
        <%= f.text_area :intro, rows: "9", placeholder: "Please write your profile here.",  class: "form-control", style: "width:100% !important;" %>
      </div>

      <div class="mx-auto text-left" style="font-size:11px;color:#BBBBBB;">
        The basis of MEEaT JAPAN is human relations. Let 's make an effort to get to know yourself. Please tell me what you like. What would you say if you are asked five things you could not live without this? What is your favorite destination, book, movie, program, music, food? Please tell me the style of your trip (commitment, style). Let people know your personality as well. What is the motto of life?
      </div>

      <div class="actions text-center mt-5 h5">
        <%= f.submit "Submit", class: "btn btn-darkorange px-5 py-2" %>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
